01:35:01.720 --> 01:35:08.739
David S. Kong: Yeah, I'll tell you, I'll tell you a dream. But before I do… onto GIFs,

1288
01:35:09.020 --> 01:35:11.780
David S. Kong: Kaito pulls out his loot, and

