01:35:12.860 --> 01:35:15.579
David S. Kong: What is the other instrument that he has? He's… he has.

1290
01:35:18.290 --> 01:35:20.809
David S. Kong: He pulls out… oh no.

1291
01:35:21.390 --> 01:35:22.890
David S. Kong: How do I not have my…

1292
01:35:23.190 --> 01:35:28.459
