Audio shared by David S. Kong: Oh, shit.

1319
01:36:43.710 --> 01:36:44.810
David S. Kong: Oh, that sucks.

1320
01:36:45.160 --> 01:36:46.290
Audio shared by David S. Kong: Oh well.

